name: HEN's Happy Halloween Community Event Poster
description:
This is the official poster for he first ever #HENHALLOWEEN HEN's Happy Halloween Community Event hosted by @Cemo, @rblbab and @Brainksy, with the tech and tools provided by @NFTbiker.  

This poster will be given away (0.01 TEZ) during the HENHALLOWEEN event only, which runs from October 27th to November 1, 2021.  All leftover NFTs will be burned at that time.
